<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .verification-code {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
      color: #3949ab;
      padding: 10px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      background-color: #e8eaf6;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .button {
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #3949ab;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      width: 200px;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding-top: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Verify Your Email</h1>
    </div>

    <p>Hello <%= @user.email %>,</p>

    <p>Thank you for signing up with MeForYou AI! To complete your registration, please verify your email address by entering the verification code below:</p>

    <div class="verification-code">
      <%= @verification_code.code %>
    </div>

    <p>Alternatively, you can click on the button below to verify your email address:</p>

    <a href="<%= @verification_url %>" class="button">Verify Email</a>

    <p>This verification code will expire in 30 minutes.</p>

    <p>If you did not create an account with MeForYou AI, please disregard this email.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>The MeForYou AI Team</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
    <p>&copy; <%= Date.today.year %> MeForYou AI. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
